title: Novicorp WinToFlash 1.1.0001
description:
Novicorp WinToFlash 1.1.0001

image

Size: 35 MB

Requires: Windows 2000 , XP, 2003, Vista, 2008, 7, 8, 8.1, 10


image

WinToFlash helps you pull over the contents of a Windows installation disk and prep the USB drive to become a bootable replacement for the optical drive.

WinToFlash help you pull over the contents of a Windows installation disk and prep the USB drive to become a bootable replacement for the optical drive. This is about so you can install your Windows from flash drive or card, HDD, etc. to your computer or netbook.

And this is not all it can do. WinToFlash can transfer your live CD or DVD to USB card, for example, BartPE. After all you can erase your USB media and format it with Windows for everyday use.


image

* Unrar with winrar/winzip. 

* Just Run to use/install...

*Enjoy!
